{"tid":2316653,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"中東諜戰 以色列情報高官遭開15槍暗殺","createTime":"2020-12-08T04:36:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-08T09:36:38.000Z","uid":295230,"like":68,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":61,"replies":[{"pid":"1edff3330c749ac25ecb49569f570874bcd918b6","tid":2316653,"uid":295230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T04:36:29.000Z","msg":"俄羅斯衛星通訊社引述伊朗Press TV報導，一名45歲男子3日早晨在以色列首都特拉維夫遭槍擊身亡，其身分為以色列情報機關「摩薩德」高級指揮官。<br />\n<br />\nPress TV報導，男子希納維3日駕車等待紅燈時，遭連續15次槍擊，多名槍手事後迅速離開現場。在社交媒體上流傳的影片、照片顯示，一輛汽車停在一處十字路口，車身可看到多個彈孔，周圍有大批警察。<br />\n<br />\n目前，以色列方面尚未對此作出回應，媒體也未對有關摩薩德官員遭槍擊進行報導。<br />\n<br />\n俄媒指出，有網友猜測，此事件是伊朗報復核子科學家法克里薩德（Mohsen Fakhrizadeh）11月27遭刺殺的行動。伊朗最高領袖哈米尼曾強烈譴責殺害法克里薩德的行為，並呼籲對殺害他的幕後黑手予以「明確懲罰」。"},{"pid":"c1bf679c0408324fe8d4c2b99502d2623463ac40","tid":2316653,"uid":295230,"like":16,"dislike":2,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T04:39:59.000Z","msg":"中東又黎了<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8de62fe18ba224ed5105d40c7c2eb5bba60ed58e","tid":2316653,"uid":295230,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T04:40:09.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://udn.com/news/story/6809/5072832\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fudn.com%2Fnews%2Fstory%2F6809%2F5072832&d=JQtp7%2BScZlazt5%2F0T0af7JhbjDs%2B%2F0Yai8vOOt2IPjE%3D&h=dfd19901\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://udn.com/news/story/6809/5072832</a>"},{"pid":"906e1155ed82ce18c057d112d6c357cd2e36f514","tid":2316653,"uid":123020,"like":61,"dislike":1,"score":60,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T04:41:13.000Z","msg":"係首都暗殺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nCls<br />\n拍做電影實好精彩"},{"pid":"c8f9f00236993cc45ad0d65501df50c81bf1b925","tid":2316653,"uid":295230,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"quote":{"pid":"906e1155ed82ce18c057d112d6c357cd2e36f514","tid":2316653,"uid":123020,"like":61,"dislike":1,"score":60,"citedB